title: American Locomotives-A Pictorial Record of Steam Power 1900-1950
description:
American Locomotives: A Pictorial Record of Steam Power 1900-1950
Bonanza Books | 1950 | English | 264 pages | PDF | 45.8 MB

Here is the pictorial history of American RAILROAD motive POWER AS IT DEVELOPED FROM 1900 â€” a continuation of the story begun with Iron Horses. From the first Atlantic and Prairie types, fifty years of progress are shown by well over 100 full-page plates, together with diagrams and descriptions. The locomotive illustrations have been carefully chosen to show milestones in improved designs and for photogenic interest. Every major railroad is represented
